        "type": "message",
        "text": "It's not impossible.  There are more \"officer\" roles than there used to be, these days, and functional role dilution has occurred over the years -- a lot of consulting firms \/ VC firms title people as \"partners\" even though they're not legally partners, and Wall Street companies love to title all of their ICs as \"Vice Presidents\" rather than \"Associates,\" to make investors feel important...",
